All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutState
    The AboutState class is responsible for creating and rendering the About state.
    Animation
    The Animation class holds all necessary data for images that should be rendered with some animations.
    Assets
    The Assets class holds all image data for the game.
    ClickListener
    The ClickListener interface is a base for mouse click actions on buttons in the game.
    Display
    The Display class controls the game's main window.
    Empty
    The Empty tile class holds data for empty tiles.
    EndState
    EndState is an abstract class responsible for creating and rendering the End states.
    Enemy
    Enemy is an abstract class for all different types of ghosts present in the game.
    EnemyPink
    EnemyPink class controls movements and rendering of the pink enemy.
    EnemyPurple
    EnemyPurple class controls movements and rendering of the purple enemy.
    EnemyRed
    EnemyRed class controls movements and rendering of the red enemy.
    EnemyYellow
    EnemyYellow class controls movements and rendering of the yellow enemy.
    Entity
    Entity is an abstract class for all different types of entities in the game.
    EntityManager
    EntityManager is a class that holds all entities present in current game.
    Food
    Food is an abstract class for all different types of food in the game.
    FoodBanana
    FoodBanana class controls rendering of the banana food.
    FoodCherry
    FoodCherry class controls rendering of the cherry food.
    FoodKiller
    FoodKiller class controls rendering of the killer food.
    FoodNormal
    FoodNormal class controls rendering of the normal food.
    FoodStrawberry
    FoodStrawberry class controls rendering of the strawberry food.
    Game
    The Game class is the main class of the HungryPacMan game responsible for running the game loop (tick and render).
    GameLauncher
    The GameLauncher class contains the main method of the Hungry PacMan game.
    GameOverState
    The GameOverState class is responsible for loading game_over image into EndState abstract class.
    GameState
    The GameState class is responsible for creating and rendering the Games state, as well as for some parts of the game itself.
    Handler
    The Handler class enables different game objects and entities to access each other when necessary.
    ImageLoader
    The ImageLoader class controls loading of images that are used in the game from resource files.
    KeyManager
    The KeyManager class is responsible for getting user keyboard input.
    LevelLoader
    The LevelLoader class controls loading of the level map from resource map file.
    Map
    The Map class is the class responsible for controlling all the game characters by calling their tick and render methods.
    MenuState
    The MenuState class is responsible for creating and rendering the Menu state.
    MouseManager
    The MouseManager class is responsible for getting user mouse input.
    Moving
    Moving is an abstract class for all different types of moving entities in the game.
    Orientation
    The Orientation enum holds data for storing information about moving entities' orientation.
    PacMan
    PacMan class controls PacMan's movements and rendering.
    RulesState
    The RulesState class is responsible for creating and rendering the Rules state.
    SpriteSheet
    The SpriteSheet inner class provides methods for slicing an image.
    State
    State is an abstract class for all different types of game states the game can be in.
    Tile
    The Tile class holds data for a single map tile.
    UserInterfaceButton
    The UserInterfaceButton class is responsible for actions and rendering of all buttons in the game.
    UserInterfaceCenteredString
    The UserInterfaceCenteredString class is responsible for actions and rendering of all labels in the game, whose texts are aligned to center.
    UserInterfaceImage
    The UserInterfaceImage class is responsible for actions and rendering of all non-play images in the game.
    UserInterfaceLabel
    The UserInterfaceLabel class is responsible for actions and rendering of all labels in the game.
    UserInterfaceManager
    The UserInterfaceManager class is responsible for updating and rendering all UI objects present in the game.
    UserInterfaceObject
    UserInterfaceObject is an abstract class for all different types of user interface elements in the game.
    Wall
    The Wall tile class holds data for wall tiles.
    WinState
    The WinState class is responsible for loading win image into EndState abstract class.
